| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0938 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ae6311c9-43b9-5c13-bd8c-20311aed5ee7"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
